### Steps to Reproduce

1. Have an OpenAPI tool server with a query parameter defined as follows:
```
{
            "name": "tags",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Tags to filter by",
            "required": false,
            "explode": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "string"
              }
            }
          }
```

2. Add the tool server to Open WebUI
3. Start a new chat with an OpenAI backend
4. Enable native function calling
5. Type a message in the chat
6. Observe the error response

